text: The Star is a computer animated movie made by Sony Pictures Animation and The Jim Henson Company. It stars the voices of Steven Yeun, Gina Rodriguez, Zachary Levi, Keegan-Michael Key, Kelly Clarkson, Patricia Heaton, Kristin Chenoweth, Tracy Morgan, Tyler Perry, and Oprah Winfrey. == References == == Other websites == * * at Sony Pictures Animation * Category:2017 computer- animated movies Category:2017 comedy movies Category:American animated movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Christmas movies Category:Sony Pictures Animation movies
